Bounded on the NE., along line 10-11 by Lot 4097-A-2, along line 1-2 by Lot 4469-A, Psd-06-060742, on the SE., along line 2-3 by Lot 4097-B, (LRC) Psd-9157 along lines 3-4-5 by Lot 4921, along line 5-6 by Lot 4058, all of Sta. Barbara Cad. 7 Extension, on the SW., along line 6-7 by Lot 4097-C, (LRC) Psd-9157, on the NW., along line 7-8 by Lot 4499-A, (LRC) Psd-9157, along lines 8-9-10 by Lot 4499-A, (LRC) Psd-9157.

